    <section anchor="appendix-b">
      <name>Appendix B: Godel and theta_critical</name>
      <t>Threshold theta_critical=0.731 is practical boundary between formal sufficiency and semantic escalation, grounded in Godel's Second Incompleteness Theorem. In sybil-10x-g1.5 trace: 30 scores, 0 below, 30 above threshold. Demonstrates stable high-confidence convergence.</t>
    </section>
  </back>
</rfc>
